snippet.title: Hyper DBZ - 5 / 5.0 - Jiren Trailer!
snippet.description:
Powerhouse and grappler Jiren enters the arena, showing his absolute dominance! Sorry that it took a LONG WAIT before you got to watch this, guys and gals! We had our work cut out for us with Jiren. Please have some more patience with us as we're continueing our dedicated work on the 5.0 build of Hyper DBZ. Stay safe everyone!
The sprites and animations seen in the video were truly a team effort. NicotineFist, Daeron, Toni, yours truly and even more have all pitched in on these, following and building on the initial work of Gate.
